{"tid":743674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：習近平愈來愈有魅力和令人欽佩","createTime":"2018-07-15T14:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T01:34:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":224,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d4f40e2f8e5005392cd538d5d720ac14ed5d49","tid":743674,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥接受英國《金融時報》（Financial Times）專訪時，盛讚近日因通過修憲，可沒有期限永續做國家主席的習近平「愈來愈有魅力、受人欽敬」（more and more charismatic and admirable）。林鄭更稱即使外界會認為她「擦鞋」，都會選習近平成為自己最欣賞的政治領袖。<br />\n<br />\n訪問期間，林鄭否認中央收緊對香港的管治，又以西班牙政府阻止加泰自治區獨立為例，中央所作的亦只是維護自己的主權。對於提出支持香港前途自決的香港眾志周庭被DQ，無法參加立法會補選，林鄭重申必須先維護「一國」才能保存「兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又稱，明白香港年輕人因為樓價高而無法置業的沮喪，因此提出「港人首置上車盤」的安排。不過，她指出2014年參與佔領運動的部分年輕人因為妒忌他人而走向極端（some young people were being &ldquo;steered towards a more radical position&rdquo; because of a feeling of jealousy: &ldquo;when other people have it, why can&rsquo;t I?&rdquo;）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於自己競逐特首時，多次被爆她生活「離地」，包括不知便利店冇廁紙買等而淪為笑柄，林鄭承認當時感到不開心和憤怒，但如今已「愈來愈不介意」（but now I really care less and less）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180314/57946194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57946194&d=KhkvPVQ3dmFaU%2FFGt6Dd2QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9d6f6b63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57946194&h=6cf11b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180314/57946194</a>"},{"pid":"f45f9b23a1838ea5ff99f9e9671a03ddf9988271","tid":743674,"uid":20241,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"奶到不能形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59670c1925f7cf46916ce5aa54de5a3aaac222d","tid":743674,"uid":44358,"like":117,"dislike":2,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"上過床，所